sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS successful_collections
FROM data_collection
WHERE collection_status = 'success';

SELECT timestamp_utc, ne_iri16
FROM atmospheric_data
WHERE data_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- Top-level missions refer to the root missions that are not associated with any spacecraft in the hierarchy; 
- Data entries represent the collection of data points gathered during each mission; 
- Instrument names signify the tools or devices used to collect the data.
